Package: tvBartSurv
Type: Package
Title: Simulation and Gibbs Sampler for Time-Varying Treatment Effects with BART Baseline Hazard
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Ningya", family = "Wang", role = c("aut","cre"),
             email = "REPLACE-ME@example.com"))
Maintainer: Ningya Wang <REPLACE-ME@example.com>
Description: Tools to simulate survival data with a time-varying binary covariate and run
    a Gibbs sampler that alternates between a log-linear BART model for subject effects and
    a spline-based baseline hazard with Metropolis-Hastings updates.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: 
    stats,
    splines,
    R2BayesX,
    loglinearBART
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
